trol Program violations. Authorizes units of local government, including home rule units, to collect charges for certain violations. Limits the power of home rule units to implement or administer its Cross-connection Control Program in a manner inconsistent with the requirements of this Act. Amends the State Mandates Act to require implementation without reimbursement. Effective immediately.", "pending_committee_id": 235, "committee": {"committee_id": 235, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "name": "Rules"}, "referrals": [{"date": "2009-02-10", "committee_id": 235, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "name": "Rules"}, {"date": "2009-02-18", "committee_id": 202, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "name": "Executive"}, {"date": "2009-03-13", "committee_id": 235, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "name": "Rules"}, {"date": "2009-03-16", "committee_id": 200, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "name": "Environment & Energy"}, {"date": "2009-04-03", "committee_id": 235, "chamber": "H", "chamber_id": 35, "name": "Rules"}], "history": [{"date": "2009-02-10", "action": "Filed with the Clerk by Rep. Linda Chapa LaVia", "chamber": "", "chamber_id": 0, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2009-02-10", "action": "First Reading", "chamber": "", "chamber_id": 0, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2009-02-10", "action": "Referred to Rules Committee", "chamber": "", "chamber_id": 0, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2009-02-18", "action": "Assigned to Executive Committee", "chamber": "", "chamber_id": 0, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2009-02-25", "action": "Added Chief Co-Sponsor Rep. Daniel J. Burke", "chamber": "", "chamber_id": 0, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2009-03-13", "action": "Rule 19(a) / Re-referred to Rules Committee", "chamber": "", "chamber_id": 0, "importance": 1}, {"date": "2009-03-16", "action": "Committee Deadline Extended-Rule 9(b) April 3, 2009", "chamber": "", "chamber_id": 0, "importance": 0}, {"date": "2009-03-16", "action": "Assigned to Environment & Energy Committee", "chamber": "", "cha